TFTP mass get utility v0.3.1

Dependencies
-----------

- gcc
- automake && autoconf
- libcurl
- libconfig
- openssl


How to build?
------------

Just run: ./build.sh


Configuration params
--------------------

savePath - absolute path to directory where save downloaded files
maxThreads - maximum threads which program fork
filesPerThread - count of downloaded files per thread
defaultTemplate - default prefix template according man 3 strftime; String with this 
                  template will be added as prefix to saved file.

sources - section which contain at least one data source configuration like that:
{
ip = "10.245.177.21"; - IP address of device from download file
file = "srkn-AP.backup"; - filename to download from given IP
saveWithTime = 1; - save file with date/time prefix like DD-MM-YYYY-HH-MM
dateTemplate = "" - prefix template, according man 3 strftime; hardcoded template - "%Y%m%d-%H%M-"
}

See example.cfg for details.

